=E2=80=9CEveryone had moved on,=E2=80=9D Paul said.

Days after walking away from the failed ER negotiations, however, ER writer=
-producer Gemmill sent Wells and Wyle a detailed pitch for The Pitt, comple=
te with character arcs and plotlines for a Pittsburgh-based emergency room =
