The =E2=80=9CDerivative Works=E2=80=9D Question

Warner Bros. TV=E2=80=99s legal strategy is likely to rely on the differenc=
es between The Pitt and the scrubbed ER reboot, and the sheer number of med=
ical dramas in the public consciousness. It=E2=80=99s clear from a review o=
f the anti-SLAPP motion that the studio=E2=80=99s lawyers at Gibson Dunn wi=
