br/><br/>As for <i>ER</i>, the dispute can be traced back to a 1994 agreeme=
nt among
Warner Bros., <b>Steven Spielberg</b>=E2=80=99s Amblin Entertainment, and C=
richton=E2=80=94a negotiation, interestingly, in which CAA represented <i>a=
ll three parties</i>. The pact, forged as NBC ordered a two-hour pilot, del=
