felt emails, including one from Wyle in February 2023 that pleaded for an a=
ccord.<br/><br/>By April 2023, Sherri had tentatively agreed to terms, but =
according to Warners, soon introduced new demands. WBTV president <b>Brett =
Paul</b> claims she insisted on approving the showrunner and all licenses=
=E2=80=94both dealbreakers. Negotiations collapsed that fall, with Warners =
asserting that the creative team had lost interest.
=E2=80=9CEveryone had moved on,=E2=80=9D Paul said.<br/><br/>Days after wal=
king away from the failed <i>ER </i>negotiations, however, <i>ER </i>writer=
